{"type":"question","id":13551,"title":"山东舰能像中途岛级CV41这样左右26度摇摆不沉吗？","uid":1552,"topics":[306],"contents":"那些说山东舰打得过中途岛级的，先讨论一下山东舰能rock and roll吗？<br>\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USS_Midway_(CV-41)#Missions_in_the_1980s\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USS_Midway_(CV-41)#Missions_in_the_1980s</a><br>\n1986年翻修后，在菲律宾外海遇上台风，左右摇晃倾斜达26度（设计最大角度为24度），最后还是没事，试问山东舰行吗？<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/aa/USS_Midway_%28CV-41%29_heavily_rolling_during_sea_trials_in_1986.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/aa/USS_Midway_%28CV-41%29_heavily_rolling_during_sea_trials_in_1986.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/aa/USS_Midway_%28CV-41%29_heavily_rolling_during_sea_trials_in_1986.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-18","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":6}